1—female holotype: habitus, lateral view; 2—male allotype: habitus, lateral view; 3—female paratype: dorsolateral view of mesosoma; 4—female holotype: dorsal view of mesosoma; 5—male allotype: S7; 6—male allotype: S8; 7—male allotype: genital capsule.
